Description_lang: Soulbinder Tuulani lost her family at a young age. Exarch Maladaar took the bright and eager draenei under his wing and raised her as his own.

name_blz.zh_TW: 追隨者： 縛魂者圖菈妮

description_blz.en_US: Soulbinder Tuulani lost her family at a young age. Exarch Maladaar took the bright and eager draenei under his wing and raised her as his own.
description_blz.es_MX: La vinculadora de almas Tuulani perdió a su familia cuando era muy joven. El exarca Maladaar tomó a la entusiasta y brillante draenei bajo su protección y la crio como una hija.
description_blz.pt_BR: A Atalmas Tuulani perdeu a família quando era nova. O Exarca Maladaar adotou a ávida draenaia, criando-a como se fosse sua filha.
description_blz.de_DE: Die Seelenbinderin Tuulani hat ihre Familie schon in jungen Jahren verloren. Exarch Maladaar hat daraufhin die intelligente und ehrgeizige Draenei unter seine Fittiche genommen und sie wie seine eigene Tochter großgezogen.
description_blz.en_GB: Soulbinder Tuulani lost her family at a young age. Exarch Maladaar took the bright and eager draenei under his wing and raised her as his own.
description_blz.es_ES: La vinculadora de almas Tuulani perdió a toda su familia cuando era joven. El exarca Maladaar acogió a la brillante draenei y la crio como propia.
description_blz.fr_FR: La lieuse d’âme Tuulani a perdu sa famille très jeune. L’exarque Maladaar a pris sous son aile cette brillante et enthousiaste draeneï et l’a élevée comme sa fille.
description_blz.it_IT: La Vincolatrice d'Anime Tuulani ha perso la propria famiglia in giovane età. L'Esarca Maladaar ha preso la giovane e brillante Draenei sotto la sua ala protettrice e l'ha cresciuta come una figlia.
description_blz.ru_RU: Стражница душ Туулани в юном возрасте потеряла семью. Экзарх Маладаар приютил способную и энергичную дренейку и вырастил ее как собственную дочь.
description_blz.ko_KR: 영혼술사 툴라니는 어린 시절에 가족을 잃었습니다. 총독 말라다르는 이 총명하고 열정적인 드레나이를 맡아 자식처럼 키웠습니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 縛魂者圖菈妮很小的時候就失去家人。瑪拉達爾主教收養了這名傑出又積極的德萊尼，將她視如己出養育長大。
description_blz.zh_CN: 缚魂者图拉妮很小的时候就失去了家人。大主教玛拉达尔收养了这名聪明活泼的小德莱尼并当做自己的孩子将她抚养长大。
